com.yerdy.services.core
Class YRDPersistence

java.lang.Object
  com.yerdy.services.core.YRDPersistence
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class YRDPersistence
extends Object
implements Serializable

iOS provides both itself and the app its supporting an interface to the keychain for persistance beyond the installation life of the app. This class is meant to provide the Android equivalent. Out the gate it will provide persistence, but not outside the life of the app.
